{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/mu9wrf","slide":7,"text":"The ask is a focused pilot, not a platform replacement.\nConnect existing campaign and case data, monitor one high-volume scam family for 30 days, and measure whether CheckVar reduces the time from first signal to customer protection.\nClose by offering the live demo: customer check, explainable result, anonymous report, then the bank operations view."}